                    <a class="button secondary small" href="https://github.com/mmgdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
                <time>2026</time>
                <a href="/notes">后台 Markdown 写作</a>
                <p>支持 Markdown 编写、图片上传、实时预览和发布流程。</p>
                <div class="card-links">
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="/notes">随笔</a>
                    <a class="button secondary small" href="https://github.com/mmgdh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>
